_sText:
This is our 3rd map from our clan, and this one is much more fun oriented than the other two maps we've uploaded. The purpose we named it spacebar is because after playing it, you will realize that your life depends heavily on how quickly u can tap your spacebar.

There is a map_config of 200 gravity in the .zip, and both spawn areas have a large ramp that shoots the player hurling through the air to wherever they want. 

For those wondering, this was originally a gg_ map but we felt it would be more widley used if converted to an fy_ map, but none the less, it still does work fine with gungame.
This has actually become quite popular on our Gun Game server @ 72.232.81.85:27015
The Candy Shoppe :: GUN GAME v3 | FastMapDL | Bullettime

this map uses buy zones, but i reccomend using the shotgun.
